程序包 edu.whu.cs.ftp.client

注释类型 NeedSpareThread

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(METHOD)
public @interface NeedSpareThread
    Annotation for informing MultiThreadFTPClientHandler. Methods annotated with NeedSpareThread will be executed on another thread. However, the result value of such annotated method isn't handled by MultiThreadFTPClientHandler, which means that such method should declare void as returned type.

    NOTE: Only methods of FTPClient interface should be annotated with NeedSpareThread, or else it makes no difference, since MultiThreadFTPClientHandler only works with interface.
